## 🟡 中危安全问题 (P2 - 建议修复)

### 5. 敏感数据日志记录 🟡

**问题描述**: 
代码可能记录敏感信息（请求内容、Token 等）

**证据**:
```typescript
// dashboard/src/utils/websocket-manager.ts:233
console.log('[WS] Sent:', message.event)
// 如果 message.data 包含敏感数据会被记录

// dashboard/src/dashboard/services/database.service.ts:149
console.log(`✅ SQL script executed successfully`);
// SQL 查询可能包含敏感数据
```

**风险等级**: 🟡 **中危**

**修复建议**:

```typescript
// ✅ 安全日志记录
import pino from 'pino';

const logger = pino({
  level: process.env.LOG_LEVEL || 'info',
  // 生产环境不记录敏感字段
  redact: {
    paths: [
      'req.headers.authorization',
      'req.headers.cookie',
      'user.password',
      'user.token',
      'data.apiKey',
      'data.secret',
      'message.data.password',
      'message.data.token'
    ],
    remove: true
  },
  // 使用结构化日志
  formatters: {
    level: (label) => ({ level: label })
  }
});

// ✅ 敏感数据脱敏
function sanitizeForLogging(data: any): any {
  const sensitiveFields = ['password', 'token', 'secret', 'apiKey', 'auth'];

  if (typeof data === 'string') {
    return data.replace(/["'](password|token|secret|apiKey|auth)["']\s*:\s*["']([^"']+)["']/gi, 
      (match, field, value) => `"${field}":"***"`);
  }

  if (typeof data === 'object' && data !== null) {
    const sanitized = { ...data };

    for (const field of sensitiveFields) {
      if (field in sanitized) {
        sanitized[field] = '***';
      }
    }

    return sanitized;
  }

  return data;
}

// ✅ 使用安全日志
logger.info({
  event: message.event,
  data: sanitizeForLogging(message.data)
}, 'WebSocket message sent');
```

